						               													<description>Forged in Fire; Southern Field Guide contains the complete army list system for the Southern Republic Army, MILICIA, Humanist Alliance Protection Force, Mekong Peacekeepers, and Eastern Sun Emirate Retinues as well as rules for fielding Mekong Mercenary Guild and AST Protectorate forces.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Forged in Fire continues the story of the War for Terra Nova and updates the timeline for the South to TN 1951.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;- Heavy Gear Blitz! Army List construction rules and shared cadres for the SRA, MILICIA, HAPF, ESEG, and MDP.&amp;#10;- Faction specific cadres and model swap lists.&amp;#10;- Rules for fielding Mercenary Guild and AST Protectorate forces.&amp;#10;- Detailed backgrounds on the Southern Leagues and their military forces.&amp;#10;- Southern Vehicle Compendium&amp;#10;- Details of the battle for Port Oasis.&amp;#10;- Miniature Gallery&amp;#10;- Datacards&amp;#10;&amp;#10;This full color 176 page book is a Field Guide for use with a copy of the most current Heavy Gear Blitz! rulebook. Dream Pod 9 miniatures, six-sided dice, and a measuring tape are also required for play.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;For two or more players, ages 8 and up.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Soft Cover, ISBN: 978-1-927334-59-1&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
